summary: There aren’t a lot of female youtubers, so: PressHeartsToContinue is one. She’s a cool dude. She played Undertale if you’re...
body:
There aren’t a lot of female youtubers, so: PressHeartsToContinue is one. She’s a cool dude. She played Undertale if you’re interested. She was one of the first ever people to play Undertale, because it came out on September 15, 2015 and she played it on October 6 2015, so literally 2 weeks after it came out, and I think that’s cool because you get fresh eyes on the game. Most youtubers only started playing it once it became popular, but she played it before it became popular.

(also, I only watched her old videos, so I don’t know what her new videos are about, I just know they’re mostly vlogs, but i don’t watch them. I only watch her gaming videos).

summary: I think I probably watch more YouTube than anything these days (if you didn’t know, my channel with my sis is Moonlight Motel...
caption:
I think I probably watch more YouTube than anything these days (if you didn’t know, my channel with my sis is Moonlight Motel and it has an IG too). I’ve mentioned some of my YouTube crushes before, mostly ASMR ladies, but here’s one that isn’t: Jenny Nicholson. She talks about all sorts of things, including movies and theme parks, and I don’t always agree with her reviews, but she’s super cool and smart, and that cute kind of awkward, and I see she collects the kind of stuff I do, ha. In fact, I badly want some of that EPCOT stuff behind her! I also love the cosplays she does for her vids! This one of Buzzy from Cranium Command is adorable! And yes, most of my crushes are much younger than me, but it’s not easy to find attractive women who share my interests that aren’t married, ha. Especially with my strong distaste for tattoos. #jennynicholson #youtube #youtubers #wcw #EPCOT #womancrushwednesday #disney #waltdisneywolf #disneybymoonlight #picoftheday #photooftheday #kawaii #kawaiiwolf #igers #iphonesia #instagood #instamood #craniumcommand #cosplay (at Austin, Texas)
https://www.instagram.com/p/Bt0sG8FHggx/?utm_source=ig_tumblr_share&igshid=18naymof506aa
